      "text": [
        ": «اَلْقُنُوتُ فِي اَلْوَتْرِ اِسْتِغْفَارٌ وَ فِي اَلْفَرِيضَةِ اَلدُّعَاءُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1411 - It is narrated by Abdur-Rahman ibn Abi Abdullah from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) that He said:\n\"The Qunoot (supplication) in the Witr prayer is for seeking forgiveness, while in the obligatory (prayers) it is for supplication (general prayers)”."
        ]
      }
